{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I was basically concerned about what was going on in the world."},{"time":3000,"text":"I couldn't understand"},{"time":5000,"text":"the starvation, the destruction,"},{"time":7000,"text":"the killing of innocent people."},{"time":9000,"text":"Making sense of those things"},{"time":11000,"text":"is a very difficult thing to do."},{"time":14000,"text":"And when I was 12, I became an actor."},{"time":17000,"text":"I was bottom of the class. I haven't got any qualifications."},{"time":20000,"text":"I was told I was dyslexic."},{"time":23000,"text":"In fact, I have got qualifications."},{"time":25000,"text":"I got a D in pottery, which was the one thing that I did get --"},{"time":27000,"text":"which was useful, obviously."},{"time":29000,"text":"And so concern"},{"time":31000,"text":"is where all of this comes from."},{"time":33000,"text":"And then, being an actor, I was doing these different kinds of things,"},{"time":36000,"text":"and I felt the content of the work that I was involved in"},{"time":38000,"text":"really wasn't cutting it, that there surely had to be more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":41000,"text":"And at that point, I read a book by Frank Barnaby,"},{"time":43000,"text":"this wonderful nuclear physicist,"},{"time":45000,"text":"and he said that media had a responsibility,"},{"time":47000,"text":"that all sectors of society had a responsibility"},{"time":50000,"text":"to try and progress things and move things forward."},{"time":52000,"text":"And that fascinated me,"},{"time":54000,"text":"because I'd been messing around with a camera most of my life."},{"time":57000,"text":"And then I thought, well maybe I could do something."},{"time":59000,"text":"Maybe I could become a filmmaker."},{"time":61000,"text":"Maybe I can use the form of film constructively"},{"time":63000,"text":"to in some way make a difference."},{"time":65000,"text":"Maybe there's a little change I can get involved in."},{"time":68000,"text":"So I started thinking about peace,"},{"time":70000,"text":"and I was obviously, as I said to you,"},{"time":72000,"text":"very much moved by these images,"},{"time":74000,"text":"trying to make sense of that."},{"time":76000,"text":"Could I go and speak to older and wiser people"},{"time":78000,"text":"who would tell me how they made sense"},{"time":80000,"text":"of the things that are going on?"},{"time":82000,"text":"Because it's obviously incredibly frightening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84000,"text":"But I realized that,"},{"time":86000,"text":"having been messing around with structure as an actor,"},{"time":88000,"text":"that a series of sound bites in itself wasn't enough,"},{"time":91000,"text":"that there needed to be a mountain to climb,"},{"time":93000,"text":"there needed to be a journey that I had to take."},{"time":95000,"text":"And if I took that journey,"},{"time":97000,"text":"no matter whether it failed or succeeded, it would be completely irrelevant."},{"time":99000,"text":"The point was that I would have something"},{"time":101000,"text":"to hook the questions of -- is humankind fundamentally evil?"},{"time":104000,"text":"Is the destruction of the world inevitable? Should I have children?"},{"time":106000,"text":"Is that a responsible thing to do? Etc., etc."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109000,"text":"So I was thinking about peace,"},{"time":111000,"text":"and then I was thinking, well where's the starting point for peace?"},{"time":113000,"text":"And that was when I had the idea."},{"time":115000,"text":"There was no starting point for peace."},{"time":117000,"text":"There was no day of global unity."},{"time":119000,"text":"There was no day of intercultural cooperation."},{"time":121000,"text":"There was no day when humanity came together,"},{"time":123000,"text":"separate in all of those things"},{"time":125000,"text":"and just shared it together --"},{"time":127000,"text":"that we're in this together,"},{"time":129000,"text":"and that if we united and we interculturally cooperated,"},{"time":132000,"text":"then that might be the key to humanity's survival."},{"time":134000,"text":"That might shift the level of consciousness"},{"time":136000,"text":"around the fundamental issues that humanity faces --"},{"time":139000,"text":"if we did it just for a day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":141000,"text":"So obviously we didn't have any money."},{"time":143000,"text":"I was living at my mom's place."},{"time":146000,"text":"And we started writing letters to everybody."},{"time":149000,"text":"You very quickly work out what is it that you've got to do"},{"time":152000,"text":"to fathom that out."},{"time":154000,"text":"How do you create a day voted by every single head of state in the world"},{"time":157000,"text":"to create the first ever Ceasefire Nonviolence Day,"},{"time":159000,"text":"the 21st of September?"},{"time":161000,"text":"And I wanted it to be the 21st of September"},{"time":163000,"text":"because it was my granddad's favorite number."},{"time":165000,"text":"He was a prisoner of war."},{"time":167000,"text":"He saw the bomb go off at Nagasaki."},{"time":169000,"text":"It poisoned his blood. He died when I was 11."},{"time":172000,"text":"So he was like my hero."},{"time":174000,"text":"And the reason why 21 was the number is"},{"time":176000,"text":"700 men left, 23 came back,"},{"time":178000,"text":"two died on the boat and 21 hit the ground."},{"time":180000,"text":"And that's why we wanted it to be the 21st of September as the date of peace."}]},{"cues":[{"time":183000,"text":"So we began this journey,"},{"time":185000,"text":"and we launched it in 1999."},{"time":187000,"text":"And we wrote to heads of state, their ambassadors,"},{"time":190000,"text":"Nobel Peace laureates, NGOs, faiths,"},{"time":192000,"text":"various organizations -- literally wrote to everybody."},{"time":195000,"text":"And very quickly, some letters started coming back."},{"time":198000,"text":"And we started to build this case."},{"time":201000,"text":"And I remember the first letter."},{"time":203000,"text":"One of the first letters was from the Dalai Lama."},{"time":205000,"text":"And of course we didn't have the money; we were playing guitars"},{"time":207000,"text":"and getting the money for the stamps that we were sending out all of [this mail]."},{"time":210000,"text":"A letter came through from the Dalai Lama saying,"},{"time":212000,"text":"\"This is an amazing thing. Come and see me."},{"time":214000,"text":"I'd love to talk to you about the first ever day of peace.\""},{"time":216000,"text":"And we didn't have money for the flight."},{"time":218000,"text":"And I rang Sir Bob Ayling, who was CEO of BA at the time,"},{"time":221000,"text":"and said, \"Mate, we've got this invitation."},{"time":223000,"text":"Could you give me a flight? Because we're going to go see him.\""},{"time":226000,"text":"And of course, we went and saw him and it was amazing."},{"time":228000,"text":"And then Dr. Oscar Arias came forward."}]},{"cues":[{"time":230000,"text":"And actually, let me go back to that slide,"},{"time":232000,"text":"because when we launched it in 1999 --"},{"time":234000,"text":"this idea to create the first ever day of ceasefire and non-violence --"},{"time":237000,"text":"we invited thousands of people."},{"time":239000,"text":"Well not thousands -- hundreds of people, lots of people --"},{"time":242000,"text":"all the press, because we were going to try and create"},{"time":244000,"text":"the first ever World Peace Day, a peace day."},{"time":246000,"text":"And we invited everybody,"},{"time":248000,"text":"and no press showed up."},{"time":250000,"text":"There were 114 people there -- they were mostly my friends and family."},{"time":253000,"text":"And that was kind of like the launch of this thing."},{"time":255000,"text":"But it didn't matter because we were documenting, and that was the thing."},{"time":258000,"text":"For me, it was really about the process."},{"time":260000,"text":"It wasn't about the end result."},{"time":262000,"text":"And that's the beautiful thing about the camera."},{"time":264000,"text":"They used to say the pen is mightier than the sword. I think the camera is."},{"time":267000,"text":"And just staying in the moment with it was a beautiful thing"},{"time":269000,"text":"and really empowering actually."}]},{"cues":[{"time":271000,"text":"So anyway, we began the journey."},{"time":273000,"text":"And here you see people like Mary Robinson, I went to see in Geneva."},{"time":276000,"text":"I'm cutting my hair, it's getting short and long,"},{"time":278000,"text":"because every time I saw Kofi Annan,"},{"time":280000,"text":"I was so worried that he thought I was a hippie that I cut it,"},{"time":283000,"text":"and that was kind of what was going on."},{"time":285000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":288000,"text":"Yeah, I'm not worried about it now."},{"time":290000,"text":"So Mary Robinson,"},{"time":292000,"text":"she said to me, \"Listen, this is an idea whose time has come. This must be created.\""},{"time":295000,"text":"Kofi Annan said, \"This will be beneficial to my troops on the ground.\""},{"time":298000,"text":"The OAU at the time, led by Salim Ahmed Salim,"},{"time":300000,"text":"said, \"I must get the African countries involved.\""},{"time":302000,"text":"Dr. Oscar Arias, Nobel Peace laureate,"},{"time":304000,"text":"president now of Costa Rica,"},{"time":306000,"text":"said, \"I'll do everything that I can.\""},{"time":308000,"text":"So I went and saw Amr Moussa at the League of Arab States."},{"time":311000,"text":"I met Mandela at the Arusha peace talks,"},{"time":313000,"text":"and so on and so on and so on --"},{"time":315000,"text":"while I was building the case"},{"time":317000,"text":"to prove whether this idea"},{"time":319000,"text":"would make sense."}]},{"cues":[{"time":321000,"text":"And then we were listening to the people. We were documenting everywhere."},{"time":324000,"text":"76 countries in the last 12 years, I've visited."},{"time":327000,"text":"And I've always spoken to women and children wherever I've gone."},{"time":329000,"text":"I've recorded 44,000 young people."},{"time":331000,"text":"I've recorded about 900 hours of their thoughts."},{"time":333000,"text":"I'm really clear about how young people feel"},{"time":336000,"text":"when you talk to them about this idea"},{"time":338000,"text":"of having a starting point for their actions for a more peaceful world"},{"time":341000,"text":"through their poetry, their art, their literature,"},{"time":343000,"text":"their music, their sport, whatever it might be."},{"time":345000,"text":"And we were listening to everybody."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347000,"text":"And it was an incredibly thing, working with the U.N."},{"time":349000,"text":"and working with NGOs and building this case."},{"time":351000,"text":"I felt that I was presenting a case"},{"time":353000,"text":"on behalf of the global community"},{"time":355000,"text":"to try and create this day."},{"time":357000,"text":"And the stronger the case and the more detailed it was,"},{"time":359000,"text":"the better chance we had of creating this day."},{"time":362000,"text":"And it was this stuff, this,"},{"time":365000,"text":"where I actually was in the beginning"},{"time":367000,"text":"kind of thinking no matter what happened, it didn't actually matter."},{"time":369000,"text":"It didn't matter if it didn't create a day of peace."},{"time":371000,"text":"The fact is that, if I tried and it didn't work,"},{"time":374000,"text":"then I could make a statement"},{"time":376000,"text":"about how unwilling the global community is to unite --"},{"time":378000,"text":"until, it was in Somalia, picking up that young girl."},{"time":381000,"text":"And this young child"},{"time":383000,"text":"who'd taken about an inch and a half out of her leg with no antiseptic,"},{"time":386000,"text":"and that young boy who was a child soldier,"},{"time":388000,"text":"who told me he'd killed people -- he was about 12 --"},{"time":391000,"text":"these things made me realize"},{"time":394000,"text":"that this was not a film that I could just stop."},{"time":397000,"text":"And that actually, at that moment something happened to me,"},{"time":400000,"text":"which obviously made me go, \"I'm going to document."},{"time":402000,"text":"If this is the only film that I ever make,"},{"time":404000,"text":"I'm going to document until this becomes a reality.\""},{"time":407000,"text":"Because we've got to stop, we've got to do something"},{"time":410000,"text":"where we unite --"},{"time":412000,"text":"separate from all the politics and religion"},{"time":414000,"text":"that, as a young person, is confusing me."},{"time":416000,"text":"I don't know how to get involved in that process."}]},{"cues":[{"time":418000,"text":"And then on the seventh of September, I was invited to New York."},{"time":421000,"text":"The Costa Rican government and the British government"},{"time":423000,"text":"had put forward to the United Nations General Assembly,"},{"time":425000,"text":"with 54 co-sponsors,"},{"time":427000,"text":"the idea of the first ever Ceasefire Nonviolence Day,"},{"time":430000,"text":"the 21st of September, as a fixed calendar date,"},{"time":433000,"text":"and it was unanimously adopted by every head of state in the world."},{"time":436000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":443000,"text":"Yeah, but there were hundreds of individuals, obviously, who made that a reality."},{"time":447000,"text":"And thank you to all of them."},{"time":449000,"text":"That was an incredible moment."},{"time":451000,"text":"I was at the top of the General Assembly just looking down into it and seeing it happen."},{"time":453000,"text":"And as I mentioned, when it started,"},{"time":455000,"text":"we were at the Globe, and there was no press."},{"time":457000,"text":"And now I was thinking, \"Well, the press it really going to hear this story.\""},{"time":460000,"text":"And suddenly, we started to institutionalize this day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":463000,"text":"Kofi Annan invited me on the morning of September the 11th"},{"time":465000,"text":"to do a press conference."},{"time":467000,"text":"And it was 8:00 AM when I stood there."},{"time":469000,"text":"And I was waiting for him to come down, and I knew that he was on his way."},{"time":472000,"text":"And obviously he never came down. The statement was never made."},{"time":475000,"text":"The world was never told there was a day of global ceasefire and nonviolence."},{"time":478000,"text":"And it was obviously a tragic moment"},{"time":480000,"text":"for the thousands of people who lost their lives,"},{"time":482000,"text":"there and then subsequently all over the world."},{"time":485000,"text":"It never happened."},{"time":487000,"text":"And I remember thinking,"},{"time":489000,"text":"\"This is exactly why, actually,"},{"time":491000,"text":"we have to work even harder."},{"time":494000,"text":"And we have to make this day work."},{"time":496000,"text":"It's been created; nobody knows."},{"time":498000,"text":"But we have to continue this journey,"},{"time":500000,"text":"and we have to tell people,"},{"time":502000,"text":"and we have to prove it can work.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":504000,"text":"And I left New York freaked,"},{"time":506000,"text":"but actually empowered."},{"time":508000,"text":"And I felt inspired"},{"time":510000,"text":"by the possibilities"},{"time":512000,"text":"that if it did, then maybe we wouldn't see things like that."},{"time":516000,"text":"I remember putting that film out and going to cynics."},{"time":518000,"text":"I was showing the film,"},{"time":520000,"text":"and I remember being in Israel and getting it absolutely slaughtered"},{"time":522000,"text":"by some guys having watched the film --"},{"time":524000,"text":"that it's just a day of peace, it doesn't mean anything."},{"time":527000,"text":"It's not going to work; you're not going to stop the fighting in Afghanistan;"},{"time":529000,"text":"the Taliban won't listen, etc., etc."},{"time":532000,"text":"It's just symbolism."},{"time":534000,"text":"And that was even worse"},{"time":536000,"text":"than actually what had just happened in many ways,"},{"time":538000,"text":"because it couldn't not work."},{"time":543000,"text":"I'd spoken in Somalia, Burundi, Gaza, the West Bank,"},{"time":545000,"text":"India, Sri Lanka, Congo, wherever it was,"},{"time":547000,"text":"and they'd all tell me, \"If you can create a window of opportunity,"},{"time":549000,"text":"we can move aid, we can vaccinate children."},{"time":551000,"text":"Children can lead their projects."},{"time":553000,"text":"They can unite. They can come together. If people would stop, lives will be saved.\""},{"time":556000,"text":"That's what I'd heard."},{"time":558000,"text":"And I'd heard that from the people who really understood what conflict was about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":561000,"text":"And so I went back to the United Nations."},{"time":563000,"text":"I decided that I'd continue filming and make another movie."},{"time":565000,"text":"And I went back to the U.N. for another couple of years."},{"time":568000,"text":"We started moving around the corridors of the U.N. system,"},{"time":570000,"text":"governments and NGOs,"},{"time":572000,"text":"trying desperately to find somebody"},{"time":574000,"text":"to come forward and have a go at it,"},{"time":576000,"text":"see if we could make it possible."},{"time":578000,"text":"And after lots and lots of meetings obviously,"},{"time":580000,"text":"I'm delighted that this man, Ahmad Fawzi,"},{"time":582000,"text":"one of my heroes and mentors really,"},{"time":584000,"text":"he managed to get UNICEF involved."},{"time":586000,"text":"And UNICEF, God bless them, they said, \"Okay, we'll have a go.\""},{"time":588000,"text":"And then UNAMA became involved in Afghanistan."},{"time":590000,"text":"It was historical. Could it work in Afghanistan"},{"time":592000,"text":"with UNAMA and WHO"},{"time":594000,"text":"and civil society, etc., etc., etc.?"},{"time":596000,"text":"And I was getting it all on film and I was recording it,"},{"time":599000,"text":"and I was thinking, \"This is it. This is the possibility of it maybe working."},{"time":602000,"text":"But even if it doesn't, at least the door is open"},{"time":605000,"text":"and there's a chance.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":607000,"text":"And so I went back to London,"},{"time":609000,"text":"and I went and saw this chap, Jude Law."},{"time":611000,"text":"And I saw him because he was an actor, I was an actor,"},{"time":613000,"text":"I had a connection to him,"},{"time":615000,"text":"because we needed to get to the press, we needed this attraction,"},{"time":617000,"text":"we needed the media to be involved."},{"time":619000,"text":"Because if we start pumping it up a bit maybe more people would listen"},{"time":622000,"text":"and there'd be more --"},{"time":624000,"text":"when we got into certain areas,"},{"time":626000,"text":"maybe there would be more people interested."},{"time":628000,"text":"And maybe we'd be helped financially a little bit more,"},{"time":630000,"text":"which had been desperately difficult."},{"time":632000,"text":"I won't go into that."},{"time":634000,"text":"So Jude said, \"Okay, I'll do some statements for you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":636000,"text":"While I was filming these statements, he said to me, \"Where are you going next?\""},{"time":638000,"text":"I said, \"I'm going to go to Afghanistan.\" He said, \"Really?\""},{"time":640000,"text":"And I could sort of see a little look in his eye of interest."},{"time":643000,"text":"So I said to him, \"Do you want to come with me?"},{"time":645000,"text":"It'd be really interesting if you came."},{"time":647000,"text":"It would help and bring attention."},{"time":649000,"text":"And that attention"},{"time":651000,"text":"would help leverage the situation,"},{"time":653000,"text":"as well as all of the other sides of it.\""},{"time":655000,"text":"I think there's a number of pillars to success."},{"time":657000,"text":"One is you've got to have a great idea."},{"time":659000,"text":"The other is you've got to have a constituency, you've got to have finance,"},{"time":662000,"text":"and you've got to be able to raise awareness."},{"time":664000,"text":"And actually I could never raise awareness by myself, no matter what I'd achieved."},{"time":667000,"text":"So these guys were absolutely crucial."},{"time":670000,"text":"So he said yes,"},{"time":672000,"text":"and we found ourselves in Afghanistan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":674000,"text":"It was a really incredible thing that when we landed there,"},{"time":677000,"text":"I was talking to various people, and they were saying to me,"},{"time":680000,"text":"\"You've got to get everybody involved here."},{"time":682000,"text":"You can't just expect it to work. You have to get out and work.\""},{"time":685000,"text":"And we did, and we traveled around,"},{"time":688000,"text":"and we spoke to elders, we spoke to doctors, we spoke to nurses,"},{"time":691000,"text":"we held press conferences, we went out with soldiers,"},{"time":694000,"text":"we sat down with ISAF, we sat down with NATO,"},{"time":696000,"text":"we sat down with the U.K. government."},{"time":698000,"text":"I mean, we basically sat down with everybody --"},{"time":701000,"text":"in and out of schools with ministers of education,"},{"time":703000,"text":"holding these press conferences,"},{"time":705000,"text":"which of course, now were loaded with press, everybody was there."},{"time":708000,"text":"There was an interest in what was going on."},{"time":710000,"text":"This amazing woman, Fatima Gailani, was absolutely instrumental in what went on"},{"time":714000,"text":"as she was the spokesperson for the resistance against the Russians."},{"time":717000,"text":"And her Afghan network"},{"time":719000,"text":"was just absolutely everywhere."},{"time":721000,"text":"And she was really crucial in getting the message in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":723000,"text":"And then we went home. We'd sort of done it."},{"time":725000,"text":"We had to wait now and see what happened."},{"time":727000,"text":"And I got home,"},{"time":729000,"text":"and I remember one of the team bringing in a letter to me"},{"time":732000,"text":"from the Taliban."},{"time":734000,"text":"And that letter basically said, \"We'll observe this day."},{"time":737000,"text":"We will observe this day."},{"time":739000,"text":"We see it as a window of opportunity."},{"time":741000,"text":"And we will not engage. We're not going to engage.\""},{"time":744000,"text":"And that meant that humanitarian workers"},{"time":747000,"text":"wouldn't be kidnapped or killed."},{"time":750000,"text":"And then suddenly, I obviously knew at this point, there was a chance."},{"time":753000,"text":"And days later,"},{"time":755000,"text":"1.6 million children were vaccinated against polio"},{"time":758000,"text":"as a consequence of everybody stopping."},{"time":760000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":770000,"text":"And like the General Assembly,"},{"time":772000,"text":"obviously the most wonderful, wonderful moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":774000,"text":"And so then we wrapped the film up and we put it together"},{"time":776000,"text":"because we had to go back."},{"time":778000,"text":"We put it into Dari and Pashto. We put it in the local dialects."},{"time":781000,"text":"We went back to Afghanistan,"},{"time":783000,"text":"because the next year was coming, and we wanted to support."},{"time":786000,"text":"But more importantly, we wanted to go back,"},{"time":788000,"text":"because these people in Afghanistan were the heroes."},{"time":790000,"text":"They were the people who believed in peace"},{"time":793000,"text":"and the possibilities of it, etc., etc. -- and they made it real."},{"time":796000,"text":"And we wanted to go back and show them the film"},{"time":798000,"text":"and say, \"Look, you guys made this possible. And thank you very much.\""},{"time":801000,"text":"And we gave the film over."},{"time":803000,"text":"Obviously it was shown, and it was amazing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":805000,"text":"And then that year, that year, 2008,"},{"time":808000,"text":"this ISAF statement from Kabul, Afghanistan, September 17th:"},{"time":811000,"text":"\"General Stanley McChrystal,"},{"time":813000,"text":"commander of international security assistance forces in Afghanistan,"},{"time":815000,"text":"announced today ISAF will not conduct offensive military operations"},{"time":818000,"text":"on the 21st of September.\""},{"time":820000,"text":"They were saying they would stop."},{"time":822000,"text":"And then there was this other statement"},{"time":824000,"text":"that came out from the U.N. Department of Security and Safety"},{"time":827000,"text":"saying that, in Afghanistan,"},{"time":829000,"text":"because of this work,"},{"time":831000,"text":"the violence was down by 70 percent."},{"time":833000,"text":"70 percent reduction in violence on this day at least."},{"time":836000,"text":"And that completely blew my mind"},{"time":838000,"text":"almost more than anything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":840000,"text":"And I remember being stuck in New York, this time because of the volcano,"},{"time":843000,"text":"which was obviously much less harmful."},{"time":845000,"text":"And I was there thinking about what was going on."},{"time":847000,"text":"And I kept thinking about this 70 percent."},{"time":849000,"text":"70 percent reduction in violence --"},{"time":851000,"text":"in what everyone said was completely impossible"},{"time":853000,"text":"and you couldn't do."},{"time":855000,"text":"And that made me think that, if we can get 70 percent in Afghanistan,"},{"time":858000,"text":"then surely we can get 70 percent reduction everywhere."},{"time":863000,"text":"We have to go for a global truce."},{"time":865000,"text":"We have to utilize this day of ceasefire and nonviolence"},{"time":867000,"text":"and go for a global truce,"},{"time":869000,"text":"go for the largest recorded cessation of hostilities,"},{"time":872000,"text":"both domestically and internationally, ever recorded."}]},{"cues":[{"time":875000,"text":"That's exactly what we must do."},{"time":877000,"text":"And on the 21st of September this year,"},{"time":879000,"text":"we're going to launch that campaign at the O2 Arena"},{"time":881000,"text":"to go for that process,"},{"time":883000,"text":"to try and create the largest recorded cessation of hostilities."},{"time":886000,"text":"And we will utilize all kinds of things --"},{"time":888000,"text":"have a dance and social media"},{"time":890000,"text":"and visiting on Facebook and visit the website, sign the petition."},{"time":893000,"text":"And it's in the six official languages of the United Nations."},{"time":896000,"text":"And we'll globally link with government, inter-government,"},{"time":898000,"text":"non-government, education, unions, sports."},{"time":900000,"text":"And you can see the education box there."},{"time":902000,"text":"We've got resources at the moment in 174 countries"},{"time":905000,"text":"trying to get young people to be the driving force"},{"time":907000,"text":"behind the vision of that global truce."},{"time":910000,"text":"And obviously the life-saving is increased, the concepts help."}]},{"cues":[{"time":913000,"text":"Linking up with the Olympics --"},{"time":915000,"text":"I went and saw Seb Coe. I said, \"London 2012 is about truce."},{"time":917000,"text":"Ultimately, that's what it's about.\""},{"time":919000,"text":"Why don't we all team up? Why don't we bring truce to life?"},{"time":921000,"text":"Why don't you support the process of the largest ever global truce?"},{"time":924000,"text":"We'll make a new film about this process."},{"time":926000,"text":"We'll utilize sport and football."},{"time":928000,"text":"On the Day of Peace, there's thousands of football matches all played,"},{"time":931000,"text":"from the favelas of Brazil to wherever it might be."},{"time":933000,"text":"So, utilizing all of these ways"},{"time":935000,"text":"to inspire individual action."},{"time":938000,"text":"And ultimately, we have to try that."},{"time":940000,"text":"We have to work together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":942000,"text":"And when I stand here in front of all of you,"},{"time":944000,"text":"and the people who will watch these things,"},{"time":947000,"text":"I'm excited, on behalf of everybody I've met,"},{"time":949000,"text":"that there is a possibility that our world could unite,"},{"time":952000,"text":"that we could come together as one,"},{"time":954000,"text":"that we could lift the level of consciousness around the fundamental issues,"},{"time":956000,"text":"brought about by individuals."},{"time":958000,"text":"I was with Brahimi, Ambassador Brahimi."},{"time":960000,"text":"I think he's one of the most incredible men"},{"time":962000,"text":"in relation to international politics -- in Afghanistan, in Iraq."},{"time":965000,"text":"He's an amazing man."},{"time":967000,"text":"And I sat with him a few weeks ago."},{"time":969000,"text":"And I said to him, \"Mr. Brahimi, is this nuts, going for a global truce?"},{"time":972000,"text":"Is this possible? Is it really possible that we could do this?\""},{"time":974000,"text":"He said, \"It's absolutely possible.\""},{"time":976000,"text":"I said, \"What would you do?"},{"time":978000,"text":"Would you go to governments and lobby and use the system?\""},{"time":980000,"text":"He said, \"No, I'd talk to the individuals.\""},{"time":982000,"text":"It's all about the individuals."},{"time":984000,"text":"It's all about you and me."},{"time":986000,"text":"It's all about partnerships."},{"time":988000,"text":"It's about your constituencies; it's about your businesses."},{"time":990000,"text":"Because together, by working together,"},{"time":992000,"text":"I seriously think we can start to change things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":995000,"text":"And there's a wonderful man sitting in this audience, and I don't know where he is,"},{"time":998000,"text":"who said to me a few days ago -- because I did a little rehearsal --"},{"time":1001000,"text":"and he said, \"I've been thinking about this day"},{"time":1004000,"text":"and imagining it as a square"},{"time":1006000,"text":"with 365 squares,"},{"time":1008000,"text":"and one of them is white.\""},{"time":1010000,"text":"And it then made me think about a glass of water, which is clear."},{"time":1013000,"text":"If you put one drop,"},{"time":1015000,"text":"one drop of something, in that water,"},{"time":1017000,"text":"it'll change it forever."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1020000,"text":"By working together, we can create peace one day."},{"time":1022000,"text":"Thank you TED. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1024000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1027000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1029000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1033000,"text":"Thanks a lot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1035000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1037000,"text":"Thank you very much. Thank you."}]}]}